task.en: Please help me add a TODO item in this project document "Dinner with architect" with due date 11/11/2020.
task.zh: 请帮我在这个项目文档中添加一个TODO事项，就叫"Dinner with architect"，把due date设置成11/11/2020。
task.ar: يرجى مساعدتي في إضافة عنصر "TODO" في مستند المشروع هذا، بعنوان "Dinner with architect"، مع تاريخ الاستحقاق 11/11/2020.
task.ja: プロジェクト文書に「Dinner with architect」というTODO項目を追加し、期限を2020年11月11日としてください。
task.ru: Пожалуйста, помогите добавить пункт TODO в этот проектный документ с названием "Dinner with architect" и сроком выполнения 11/11/2020.

pre_command.en: osascript -e 'tell application "Pages" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Keynote" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to activate' && sleep 5 && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to make new document with properties {document template:template "Home Improvement"}'

grading_command: osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to tell table 1 of sheet 4 of document 1 to get value of cell "C3"' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "Dinner with architect" && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to tell table 1 of sheet 4 of document 1 to get value of cell "B3"' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "11 November 2020" && echo "True" || echo "False"
